{"tid":800753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚溝唔到女根本唔係條件差 係心態錯","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:59:35.000Z","uid":81891,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4e44d34924d6a01bf7dad7c55dcfb9177df064","tid":800753,"uid":81891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"久經驗證既追女仔方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/799676\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/799676</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n睇完呢個po見到好多回覆都係話打飛機出篤精仲簡單<br />\n<br />\n根本由一開始你地溝女就係為咗扑嘢  扑嘢為咩啊  就係出篤精  <br />\n屌你老母抱住咁嘅心態識女 係女都覺得你地毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想識女朋友第一步就要擴闊社交圈子  啫係識朋友<br />\n一識到女性 第一步就諗住扑嘢  係女都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地當識朋友  熟咗先再睇有無機會發展  先係正確識女朋友嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n諗撚住扑嘢嘅真係去叫雞打飛機算  <br />\n社交同拍拖唔適合毒撚"},{"pid":"d48f8c6d28d5fcb61af0f8e4dd517d23766537fc","tid":800753,"uid":181905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/144229_02179a66707f25ea8af55c902819ef67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F144229_02179a66707f25ea8af55c902819ef67.jpg&h=6c3fcc70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fdbdbe17b1ab91a3c7d279e7c4ab8ecce58d4b2","tid":800753,"uid":106468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"反而覺得熟左就難d做到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人好多時一下就分到一個男人係可以做朋友定做情人"},{"pid":"659bdd1430f67a602dafe69fa26b73963d14e324","tid":800753,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"我連同人相處都覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3884e17c550e217e335dc0329b26456e1fa04314","tid":800753,"uid":204717,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"事實成個社交市場就係一個A字型金字塔<br />\n有條件既人上金字塔頂互相痴埋一齊打友誼波日日扑野<br />\n底層無條件既豬閪醜男就互相排斥愈差愈遠<br />\n<br />\n所以你會成日見到柒毒男群返柒毒男 豬閪群返豬閪<br />\n而靚仔靚女係上層日日扑野<br />\n咪形成比班柒毒男溝女=扑野既感覺囉<br />\n<br />\n事實上柒毒男比多一千斤努力都唔會埋得到金字塔頂堆<br />\n豬閪亦同理<br />\n自暴自棄係好正常亦都合乎機會成本原則既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50da8c628c91515d389dff8a744683ec88f46f6f","tid":800753,"uid":81891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4fdbdbe17b1ab91a3c7d279e7c4ab8ecce58d4b2","tid":800753,"uid":106468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"反而覺得熟左就難d做到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人好多時一下就分到一個男人係可以做朋友定做情人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"但唔會係一開波諗住扑嘢嘅心態會識到女囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93777cca93f41d643f2760b73f233e33f9806a7","tid":800753,"uid":81891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"659bdd1430f67a602dafe69fa26b73963d14e324","tid":800753,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"我連同人相處都覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"咁無問題啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題係唔鍾意同人相處又怨無女個啲"},{"pid":"0f0b88ba478224bfe7a197300dfb9bc083c52c6b","tid":800753,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"J到成身毒氣，全無精氣神，點會溝到女"},{"pid":"9c8f81a8c7d27570c335fbe96d95758895f9efa0","tid":800753,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"毒撚想溝女仲算唔算毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff3932976f98ef29d2c2febd1d7ce52076ad525","tid":800753,"uid":10646